{"tid":676913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西貢黑幫血戰　刀劈車撞多人浴血","createTime":"2018-05-24T18:17:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T06:22:55.000Z","uid":48,"like":84,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"f8f69de59719afb75f22d0785ddf27c8d01ab90b","tid":676913,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T18:17:54.000Z","msg":"西貢翠塘路發生懷疑黑幫血戰，昨（24日）晚11時許，一批逾10名大漢，分乘多輛私家車及一輛拖車到達露天停車場一間酒家對開，各人手持刀棍下車，向在場約10名大漢施襲，一時間喊殺聲響徹寧靜的街道，逾20人追逐毆鬥，有人竟開車追撞人，其中拖車用車尾撞向數輛私家車，亦有一輛私家車高速衝前，撞向先前被撞的私家車，有人取起垃圾桶亂掟，場面混亂，多輛私家車被撞至橫七豎八，嚴重損毀。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息稱，遇襲一方頑抗，有人揮刀向施襲者追斬，多人浴血，大批警員接報手持伸縮警棍到場，眾大漢慌忙四散，有人跳落岸邊靠泊的小艇，擬由水路逃走，警員亦跳下艇追逐，其他警員迅速控制場面。初步至少有3人受傷，血流披面，由救護車送院救治，警員當場拘捕一人。據悉，涉案者分別屬於2個黑幫，警方仍封鎖現場，在區內追緝在逃者，並正調查事件起因。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180525/photo/bkn-20180525001558001-0525_00822_001_11b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180525%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180525001558001-0525_00822_001_11b.jpg&h=ae90f1eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/021751_6212a32834c29f0a6caa41bcdd4579f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F021751_6212a32834c29f0a6caa41bcdd4579f8.jpg&h=3d8fe7bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/021752_98366044cfd7d1f4af35c7efbae76249.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F021752_98366044cfd7d1f4af35c7efbae76249.jpg&h=b560bbcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/021752_5e150b5503d96c69229ad63286749388.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F021752_5e150b5503d96c69229ad63286749388.jpg&h=11081c00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/021752_d2b9dc4f5a8f3f7bec5222